22:23.000Z","msg":"班藍絲盲撐嗰陣又笑鳩人無腦<br />\n到而家有人指證時候又羡慕人地盲撐團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300ca47f8714bce7cb94c5ae4a79ea7c6e86dec1","tid":1977193,"uid":198414,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"香港人有咁既氣焰日日追擊差佬港共就好<br />\n不過批鬥自己人就叻 哂鳩氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運動已完 批鬥部隊已全面進場 可以做番港豬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341107769fdd27999f84c8368d60cb669d54005a","tid":1977193,"uid":321913,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"300ca47f8714bce7cb94c5ae4a79ea7c6e86dec1","tid":1977193,"uid":198414,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"香港人有咁既氣焰日日追擊差佬港共就好<br />\n不過批鬥自己人就叻 哂鳩氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n運動已完 批鬥部隊已全面進場 可以做番港豬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/157635725638392/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffans.hkgolden%2Fvideos%2F157635725638392%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppehckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=8bc0880f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/157635725638392/</a><br />\n<br />\n懵撚<br />\n自己睇啦<br />\n我都望佢係自己人呀<br />\n<br />\n你問我&ldquo;信手足vs信龍門&rdquo;<br />\n我只會信出黎搵命搏嘅手足<br />\n而到宜家都唔知係唔係選民嘅張生？<br />\n張生你都係同我返印度食蕉啦"},{"pid":"d5defec8db01b321955dee1776a4d5e8a55f74a1","tid":1977193,"uid":321913,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T17:11:31.000Z","msg":"項明生扮黃可以屌<br />\n龍門扮黃唔撚屌得？<br />\n<br />\n我屌晒你地班連衛兵<br />\n無撚晒獨立思考<br />\n而家幾多黃店屌柒佢呀<br />\n一隻手掌拍得響？<br />\n張俊傑先至係黃圈？<br />\n其他黃店老闆就唔洗理？<br />\n屌龍門就成個黃圈收皮？<br />\n我屌晒你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif